- content_for :title, "Review submissions leaderboard"

- content_for :breadcrumbs
  ol class="breadcrumb"
    li class="breadcrumb-item"
      = link_to "Leaderboards", page_path("leaderboards")
    li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page"
      | Review submissions leaderboard

div class="fpc-hint alert alert-secondary"
  p
    ' You can add reviews for all inks in the system. The most useful reviews to
    ' add would however be those from
    = link_to 'this list', missing_reviews_path
    '  as none of the inks listed there have any review.
  p Note that you need to be logged in if you want to add reviews.

= cache params[:id], expires_in: 1.hour do
  ol class="fpc-leaderboard"
    - LeaderBoard.ink_review_submissions.each do |user_data|
      = render partial: "leaderboard_row", locals: { user_data: user_data }
